songs.title: Bitches And Money
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
I’m bout to make it rain
All 2 dollar bills
Westside!
Girls, currency [x6]
Fuck this shit man

[Hook]
I got money, I got bitches
I got bitches, I got money
I got money, I got bitches
I got bitches, I got money
I got money, money gets me bitches
Bitches get my money
I got money, I got bitches
I got bitches, I got money
I got money, bitches, bitches, money
Money, bitches, bitches, bitches
I got money, money, bitches, bitches
Bitches get me money
I got money, I got bitches
I got bitches, get me money

[Verse 1]
All this money pour in, all these hoes go in
All this green around me like a nigga lawn mowing (John Deere)
Some Illuminati clothing, a fresh man goes in
Shitting on these hoes cause I ain’t have a pot to go in
Sonning all these niggas like “Luke I am your father” (bitch)
All these hoes give me head like the scar in Harry Potter
Threw 400 so I'm throwing 500 fivers
Slapping bitches up, hands full of baby powder
I’m a motherfucking coon, sitting in the room
Fucking all these bitches, like I am Bill Clinton
Money by the minute, I put it on the mitten
If money gets me bitches, bitches bring me all my digits

[Hook]

[Verse 2]
Bout to fuck a pair of twins, all geminis (hell yeah)
Thought I was fucking 8 hoes at the same time
She gave me brain, mouth on my head
So you could say, she was on my mind
I ain’t got to say shit, like a fucking mime
Cause you know I got them white faces like I roll with mimes
When I step in this bitch I blow like a landmine
You can go ahead and hate I really don’t mind
Rolling, getting baked from Whitney, Sidney, and Britney
Counting all these white faces, grand [?] and [?]
Give me ramen noodles, I don’t fuck with the Beni’s
And your motherfucking fork was worth every penny penny

[Hook]

[Bridge]
(School these hoes)
You want to go to the movies, bitch you heard of bootleg?
I ain’t buying shit!
You want to go out [?], bitch you heard of ramen noodles?
I ain’t buying shit!
Ho, I ain’t buying shit! [x3]
I said I ain’t buying shit!
Ho, I ain’t buying shit! [x3]
I said I ain’t buying shit!

[Hook]
